title: Off White Striped Jacquard Textured Premium Giza Cotton Kurta
story_description:

comfortably chic look for your next family occasion or any family outing. Comfortable and breathable

this kurta and style your look with mojari or jutti.

title: Hampton Cream Jacquard Textured Premium Giza Cotton Kurta

with churidar pyjama and stylish leather sandals for a perfect ethnic look.
